**Innovative Security Solutions was named "Best Firearms Academy in Albuquerque" three years in a row!!!**<br>
<br>
Innovative Security Solutions provides Security Training by Professional Security Instructors and is the premier Training Academy in New Mexico.<br>
<br>
ISS is the **only** Training Academy to train it's Students for success and the **only** Training Academy to offer Job Placement Assistance. We work with 15 different Security Companies to assist you in finding employment after completing the classes.<br>
<br>
The ISS Staff will train you at a fast and challenging pace, from Level 1 to Level 3 and Firearms Classes.<br>
<br>
Level 1 the Security Officer will learn the basics of Report Writing, Professionalism and the Legal Aspects of being a Security Officer.<br>
<br>
Level 2 carries equipment as well as the legal aspects of force. Here the Officer learns baton, O.C. handcuffs and empty hand defensive tactics to safely and effectively carry out their duties on the streets. The final requirement is the O.C. spray course requiring the officers to complete tasks after contamination so the Student knows that they can deal with the Pepper Spray if cross-contamination happens.<br>
<br>
At Level 3, you will shoot various drills and warm-ups prior to qualification. The final Qual meets State requirements but is done in an interactive manner which requires more out of the Security Officer.<br>
<br>
If you are looking for great training or tired of falling asleep and dreaming of challenging relevant training give ISS a call. I guarantee that you will not be disappointed. ISS is a Professional Academy and we are determined to provide you with realistic and relevant training provided by Subject Matter Experts in the fields being taught.<br>
<br>
Unlike other "lecturers", ISS Instructors are available to conduct Training on a bi-weekly basis to be able to accommodate your schedule.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Class Costs: <br>
$100/Level 1<br>
$130/Level 2<br>
$165/Level 3<br>
Cost of All Three Classes is Only $300<br>
<br>
Visit our website for Training Schedule<br>
<br>
Call us at 505-507-1630 us for more information and to Register for your Training Classes.<br>
Visit <a href="http://www.innovativesecuritysolutions.co" rel="nofollow">http://www.innovativesecuritysolutions.co</a>  for more information.  Like us on Facebook <a href="https://www.facebook.com/ISSTraining" rel="nofollow">https://www.facebook.com/ISSTraining</a>!    </section>

